            Professions and communities
            Communities of practice
            Our communities of practice meet regularly to discuss work, learn, share and support each other.







        Every Thursday between 1pm and 4pm is protected profession-time and is your time to learn and share.


        Each profession runs sessions differently, but each one usually covers a talk, design crits or a learning session.

        Meetings are 1pm to 2pm and rotate between professions on a weekly basis.

         Join the profession channels on Slack and ask for an invite if you want to come along to one.


